MODULE USER_COMMAND_0100 INPUT.

  CASE OK_CODE.

    WHEN 'SAVE'.

      PERFORM UCOMM_SAVE.

  ENDCASE.

ENDMODULE.




*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

*&      Module  EXIT_COMMAND  INPUT

*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

*       text

*----------------------------------------------------------------------*




MODULE EXIT_COMMAND INPUT.

  CASE OK_CODE.

    WHEN 'BACK' OR 'CANC'.

      LEAVE TO SCREEN 0.

    WHEN 'EXIT'.

      LEAVE PROGRAM.

  ENDCASE.

ENDMODULE.